text: tavada numbala numbalage paramadhipatigen samava ayæda pasu va pascattapa vi ohu veta yomu viya yutuya. niyama karana lada kalayak dakva, ohu numbalata suvapahasu jivanopayan bhukti vidinnata salasvayi. bhagyavanta sæma kenekutama ohuge bhagyaya ohu pirinamayi. namut ovun hæri giye nam evita niyata vasayenma numbala veta mahatvu dinayaka danduvama gæna mama biya vemi
